=== 癲癇問題 ===
[[File:Incredibles_2_screenslaver_screen.jpg|thumb]]
許多的殘疾人權利倡導者，包括{{link-en|癲癇基金會|Epilepsy Foundation|美國癲癇基金會}}對強烈燈光效果的場景提出關注，特別是彈力女超人與螢幕魔人戰鬥的場景，會令觀眾引起{{link-en|光敏感性癲癇症|Photosensitive epilepsy}}患者發作<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.cnet.com/news/incredibles-2-posts-flashing-lights-warning-for-fans-with-epilepsy/|title=Incredibles 2 posts flashing-lights warning for fans with epilepsy|last=|first=|date=2018-06-18|work=CNET|access-date=2018-06-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180618210800/https://www.cnet.com/news/incredibles-2-posts-flashing-lights-warning-for-fans-with-epilepsy/|archive-date=2018-06-18|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2018/06/18/movies/incredibles-2-seizures-epilepsy.html|title=‘Incredibles 2’ Moviegoers Warned About Possible Seizures|last=|first=|date=|work=The New York Times|access-date=2018-06-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180619141730/https://www.nytimes.com/2018/06/18/movies/incredibles-2-seizures-epilepsy.html|archive-date=2018-06-19|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.epilepsy.com/release/2018/6/epilepsy-foundation-advises-viewer-caution-related-flashing-lights-incredibles-2-and|title=Epilepsy Foundation Advises Viewer Caution Related to "Incredibles 2"|last=|first=|date=|website=Epilepsy Foundation|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180620232012/https://www.epilepsy.com/release/2018/6/epilepsy-foundation-advises-viewer-caution-related-flashing-lights-incredibles-2-and|archive-date=2018-06-20|dead-url=no|access-date=2018-06-20}}</ref>。事後，幾家的電影院張貼有關的警告標語<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.cnn.com/2018/06/18/health/incredibles-2-seizures-warning-bn/index.html|title='Incredibles 2': Theaters post warnings due to seizure concerns|last=CNN|first=Jacqueline Howard,|date=|work=CNN|access-date=2018-06-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180619161839/https://www.cnn.com/2018/06/18/health/incredibles-2-seizures-warning-bn/index.html|archive-date=2018-06-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>。迪士尼向[[今日美國|今日美國]]發表了一則聲明，指他們對電影院製作警告標語的做法表示讚賞，並要求電影院向觀眾發出一份備忘錄，警告觀眾相關的場面可能會導致身體不適<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/life/movies/2018/06/17/disney-issues-epilepsy-seizure-warning-incredibles-2/708879002/|title=Disney issues seizure warning about 'Incredibles 2' for fans with epilepsy|last=|first=|date=|work=USA TODAY|access-date=2018-06-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180620234946/https://www.usatoday.com/story/life/movies/2018/06/17/disney-issues-epilepsy-seizure-warning-incredibles-2/708879002/|archive-date=2018-06-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

針對該聲明，英國發布了重新編輯的版本<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bbfc.co.uk/releases/incredibles-2-film-2 |title=INCREDIBLES 2 [Re-edited Version,Includes short film BAO,3D]
|website=BBFC|publisher=[[英國電影分級委員會|英國電影分級委員會]]|accessdate=2018-06-11|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180611024117/https://rottentomatoes.com/m/incredibles_2|archivedate=2018-06-11}}</ref>，所有受影響的序列都有所改變，因此任何閃光燈或頻閃效果的場面現在都通過了測試<ref>{{cite tweet|user=veron4ica|last=Lewis|first=Veronica|number=1015310445098536961|title= I received this email from BBFC confirming #Incredibles2 in UK has been modified to not include the intense flashing scenes. While I only requested a warning to be posted at theaters in the US, I am glad Disney UK is looking out for its viewers with photosensitive conditions |date=2017-07-06|access-date=2017-07-21}}</ref>。中国大陆放映时为原版本，但在放映前向观众播映相关提示<ref>[http://news.mtime.com/2018/06/21/1581736.html 光敏&癫痫患者慎看《超人总动员2》] {{Wayback|url=http://news.mtime.com/2018/06/21/1581736.html |date=20181111133701 }} Mtime时光网.2018-06-21.[2018-08-31]</ref>。

